# Agent Founder

Desktop app for managing autonomous AI coding agents powered by Claude Code.

## Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React 19 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS v4 + Vite 6
- **Backend**: Rust + Tauri 2
- **Database**: SQLite (via rusqlite)
- **Font**: Geist (loaded via CDN)
- **Icons**: lucide-react

## Architecture

- `src/` — React frontend (views, components, hooks, lib, types)
- `src-tauri/src/` — Rust backend (commands, models, db, state, process pool)
- `src/lib/api.ts` — frontend wrapper for Tauri `invoke()` calls
- `src/lib/wizardConstants.ts` — shared constants for create/import wizard flows
- `src/types/index.ts` — all TypeScript interfaces
- `.founder/` — per-agent workspace directory (SOUL.md, MISSION.md, STATE.md, etc.)

## Key Patterns

- Views in `src/views/` — full-page components rendered by `App.tsx` router
- Single sidebar + main content layout via flex in `App.tsx`
- State lives in `App.tsx` (selected agent, current view) — views are stateless re: navigation
- Tauri commands defined in `src-tauri/src/commands.rs`, registered in `lib.rs`
- CSS variables defined in `src/index.css` `:root` for theming (warm neutral palette)
- Tailwind v4 imported via `@import "tailwindcss"` — no tailwind.config needed
